VoiceDir1.121C9F: The memory is fresh and painful.
Line1.121C9F: Truthfully, no. Maugan's Folly is a stain on the Zakarum's history and a reminder of my own mistakes. But I must return to collect my master's armor.
Line15.121C9F: Without her armor, I cannot continue her name. I cannot be a crusader. Her name dies and everything she fought for dies with it.
